surv_object <- Surv(time = data$futime, event = data$fustat)
fit <- survfit(surv_object ~ rx, data = ovarian)
ggsurvplot(fit, data = ovarian, pval = TRUE, conf.int = TRUE, risk.table = TRUE, 
    risk.table.col = "strata", linetype = "strata", surv.median.line = "hv", risk.table.y.text = FALSE)

fit1 <- survfit(surv_object ~ resid.ds, data = data)
fit2 <- survfit(surv_object ~ ecog.ps, data = data)
ggsurvplot(fit1, data = data, pval = TRUE, conf.int = TRUE, risk.table = TRUE, risk.table.col = "strata", 
    linetype = "strata", surv.median.line = "hv", risk.table.y.text = FALSE)

ggsurvplot(fit2, data = data, pval = TRUE, conf.int = TRUE, risk.table = TRUE, risk.table.col = "strata", 
    linetype = "strata", surv.median.line = "hv", risk.table.y.text = FALSE)
